{"id":5815,"date":"2024-05-20T10:16:24","date_gmt":"2024-05-20T00:16:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/?post_type=help_centre&#038;p=5815"},"modified":"2024-05-20T10:42:09","modified_gmt":"2024-05-20T00:42:09","slug":"installing-the-underboard-receiver","status":"publish","type":"help_centre","link":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/help-centre\/installation\/installing-the-underboard-receiver\/","title":{"rendered":"Installing the Underboard Receiver"},"content":{"rendered":"<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Installing Your Underboard Receiver\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/zsoaEZlROc4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure><p>Congratulations on grabbing the new underboard receiver. Swapping it over is simple; just follow these steps!<\/p><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Everything you\u2019ll need:<\/h4><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Main unit<\/li>\n\n<li>New underboard receiver<\/li>\n\n<li>Set of Allen keys (included in the kit)<\/li>\n\n<li>Thin plastic item (e.g., credit card)<\/li><\/ul><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step-by-step installation guide:<\/h4><ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Identify the rubber seal covering the area where the receiver is installed.<\/li>\n\n<li>Insert the thin plastic item (e.g., credit card) under the rubber seal and gently pry it out.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n<li>Locate the screw and two connectors underneath the rubber seal and use the third smallest Allen key from the kit to unscrew and remove the plate covering the connectors. Set the plate aside.<\/li>\n\n<li>Carefully disconnect the two connectors. Avoid pulling on the cables excessively to prevent damage.<\/li>\n\n<li>Gently pull the connectors apart (it may take a few attempts). Take extra care not to pull the smaller cable out of the main unit.<\/li>\n\n<li>Take the connector from the new underboard receiver and align the white dot on the connector with the corresponding white dot on the main unit&#8217;s connector.<\/li>\n\n<li>Reverse the process: guide the cable back into the cable guide and secure the plate with the screw.<\/li>\n\n<li>Use the Allen key to screw the plate back into place.<\/li>\n\n<li>Replace the rubber seal by gently pressing it into position along the edge. Ensure it is aligned correctly.<\/li><\/ol><p>We recommend double-checking that all components are securely in place and aligned properly. Once that is done, you&#8217;re ready to hit the water!<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Congratulations on grabbing the new underboard receiver. Swapping it over is simple; just follow these steps! Everything you\u2019ll need: Step-by-step installation guide: We recommend double-checking that all components are securely in place and aligned properly. Once that is done, you&#8217;re ready to hit the water!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-5815","help_centre","type-help_centre","status-publish","hentry","help_centre_category-installation"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre\/5815","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/help_centre"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/help_centre\